---
alwaysApply: true
---

- Default to App Router and Server Components.
- Use "use client" only when interactivity or browser APIs are needed.
- Use client-side fetching (SWR/React Query) only for real-time or user-specific data.
- Image: always next/image. Links: always next/link.
- Use loading.tsx/error.tsx for route-level states. Inline for component-level.
- No hardcoded secrets. Use env variables.
